。</p><p>事实上，围巾又被扔回舞台，促使乐队走开。据悉，演唱会持续了约90分钟，多首曲目尚存。</p><p>马德里人群中的几位成员在 X/Twitter 上对 Sleaford Mods 做出了回应，表达了他们对乐队立场的支持，并分享了他们对演出的喜爱程度。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我坐在前排，就在戴着围巾的“女士”旁边……她的行为非常糟糕且令人无法容忍。可惜的是，演出太棒了。希望将来能在马德里见到您。威廉姆森！</p><p> - jaimediezaguirr (@jaimediezaguirr) <a href="https://twitter.com/jaimediezaguirr/status/1720586420501217472?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 3 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">很棒的演出！！我当时坐在前排，这真是令人难以置信，但令人难过的是有人只是这么做。不管发生了什么，我希望你在马德里过得愉快并且你想回来！</p><p> — Angela Mozas (@angela_mzs) <a href="https://twitter.com/angela_mzs/status/1720593152426312040?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 4, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Everyone is entitled to saying &quot;I just don&#39;t know&quot;, not having an opinion or not sharing it. We seem to have forgotten how to respect that. Great gig.</p><p> — Klaus von Richardsson (@kvonrichardsson) <a href="https://twitter.com/kvonrichardsson/status/1720578843625295901?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 3, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Absolutely smashed it tonight fellas. On top form and such a shame it had to be cut short. See you both in Manchester!</p><p> — Nathan Moran (@NathMoranPhysio) <a href="https://twitter.com/NathMoranPhysio/status/1720581732515164509?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 3, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Sleaford Mods recently 